        "title": "Good Documentation Practices",
        "clause_number": "7.8",
        "requirement_text": "No handwritten changes or corrections shall be made to the printed text of an approved GMP document; if correction is needed on an authorized printed copy, it shall be addressed through the Error Rectification Form.",
